These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, august
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris
1. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Birthday         | august | october |
| Flower     | begonia | iris    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, turquise
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku  |
| Color           | turquise         | emerald     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, march
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
City: new-york, miami
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Birthday         | march | may    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| City   | new-york         | miami    |

