.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, japanese
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the japanese is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Pet      | goldfish     | turtle |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | japanese         |

