The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, reggae
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4
3. the fan of reggae is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | writing      | filmmaking |
| Cigar           | old-henry    | oliveros |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | epic       |
| Music-Genre     | gospel      | reggae    |

