.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, malaysian
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, classical
1. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the fan of reggae is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Nationality    | argentine | malaysian    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | classical     |

 